{
  "stem": "2230.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes when I think of all the other people that went before me, I don't think so.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But I guess that's me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We-- and one day I was taken out of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Buchenwald, taken to a arbeitslager, a place called Rothenburg on the Tauber.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You asked me if I got together with anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I got together with one guy who taught me Italian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was the Italian prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we-- we came in into this camp, just a working camp, no concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By that, I mean no gas chamber or something like that.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were building a bunker in a huge hill to put a factory in there to build airplanes or parts, I guess.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Rothenburg is up on a hill.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Tauber, which is a big river, is on the bottom.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And what we had to do is fill up pushcarts of stones from the-- from the hole and push it down to the river, to the Tauber, fill it up, pull it downstream a few kilometers, unload it, come back.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every time you went down the hill, you'd go up the hill.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Our rations was-- I mean, when I came out of camp, I was 90 pounds.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll tell you what it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Now, it's a beautiful town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Nobody knows nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was there I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But that wasn't bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You just got beat up if you didn't work hard.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
